description: The Austin, 2017-2018 construction! This ground level unit is located in the heart of South Boston. 2bed/2bath with 1,370 square feet of living space. This condo is one of a kind and certainly makes a bold statement. Thermador appliances, Cambria Calacatta Quartz countertops and backsplashes, custom moldings and carpentry including custom Hunter Douglas window shutters, high-end hydro air HVAC/hot water systems, Hans Grohe plumbing fixtures, stackable washer/dryer in-unit, two elevators in building, and a raised courtyard with two built-in gas grills are just some of the outstanding features you will find here. 2 garage parking spaces (one with EV charging station)! One pet is allowed per the condo regulations. Come make this beautiful condo your home!
